# Server Explorer configuration
#
# Copy this file to .server-explorer.conf and fill in your values.
# .server-explorer.conf is gitignored so your local settings stay local.

# HTTP proxy for package index commands (apt update, dnf check-update) on remote servers
# sitting behind private subnets. Most servers already have this configured in their
# package manager settings — this is a fallback for those that don't.
# Common in .ac.uk environments behind JANET proxies.
# Note: KEV and EPSS lookups run locally and do not need this proxy.
# proxy=http://wwwcache.example.ac.uk:8080
